@host = http://localhost:5191

### Listar contas
GET {{host}}/api/contas
Accept: application/json

### Criar conta
POST {{host}}/api/contas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeTitular": "Maria Souza",
  "cpf": "529.982.247-25",
  "status": 1
}

### Obter por Id (troque o GUID por um retornado na criação)
GET {{host}}/api/contas/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

### Atualizar (status 2 = Inativa)
PUT {{host}}/api/contas/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeTitular": "Maria S. Souza",
  "status": 2
}

### Remover
DELETE {{host}}/api/contas/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### CPF inválido -> 400
POST {{host}}/api/contas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeTitular": "Fulano",
  "cpf": "111",
  "status": 1
}
